No. 09-9275. Gregory Charles Krug, Petitioner v. John Paul Stevens, Associate Justice, Supreme Court of the United States, et al. 559 U.S. 1045, 130 S. Ct. 2079,

176 L. Ed. 2d 430,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 2882. March 29, 2010.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the District of Columbia Circuit denied.

Justice Stevens took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.

Same case below, 309 Fed. Appx. 423.
